      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/big-hedge-funds-call-doctors-scientists-an-edge-pharma-sources-say-2024-12-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[八位消息人士向路透社透露，全球一些最大的对冲基金正在招聘医生、科学家和分析师，以便在制药业股价大幅波动后为其提供关于制药股前景的专业见解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/big-hedge-funds-call-doctors-scientists-an-edge-pharma-sources-say-2024-12-04/</guid>
